title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Adrian Heath/Dan Hayes/Kevin Falness/Jeff Reuter
description: Nordo starts the show off talking to Adrian Heath, head coach of the MN United, about the Loons season in the MLS Is Back Tournament.  Dan Hayes of The Athletic breaks down the Twins roster for the impending 60 game season.  Kevin Falness calls in to discuss what the MN Wild broadcasts will look and sound like.  Finally, The Athletic's Jeff Reuter has a conversation with Nordo about the moment MLS is having right now.
